{"tid":2308963,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黎智英及兩名壹傳媒高層被控詐騙 明早西九龍裁判法院提堂","createTime":"2020-12-02T08:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T15:29:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c7b6053ab411e8cbbf19b275066b79e48ef48a27","tid":2308963,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T08:32:01.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】消息指，壹傳媒集團創辦人黎智英，以及兩名集團高層，將被落案控告詐騙罪，明日在西九龍裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n黎智英、壹傳媒集團營運總裁兼財務總監周達權、行政總監黃偉強今日到旺角警署報到。消息指，他們被落案控告詐騙罪，案件將會明早在西九龍裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n黎智英及周達權早前因違反國安法，涉嫌勾結境外勢力、危害國家安全被捕，三人亦涉及一項串謀詐騙罪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=415091\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415091&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2eQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=458a6937\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415091&h=b4de11af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=415091</a>"},{"pid":"ca7d70a31b8d37e6a37ca2d09b914bc345e7197d","tid":2308963,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T08:32:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a186a670b1c8e0f669cfa6af1e859321aa9e9cd","tid":2308963,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T08:33:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ecb44301da410d6a730368d18bab057a670853b2","tid":2308963,"uid":79117,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T08:33:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72ffe4a73dd21e13fab020ec8e58a8b0c5d2ce3b","tid":2308963,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T08:34:35.000Z","msg":"入定0282撐肥佬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\